ridge.org/core/books/before-the-west/78E4B5CE511AA928B2C650AF1CDFE3CA" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener"><em>Before the West: the Rise and Fall of Eastern World Orders</em></a> (2022).</p></span></div><br/><div class="sc-3ddd79c0-9 eACYrZ"><p>Edited by<a href="/users/samhaselby" class="sc-2e8621ab-1 jexetL">Sam Haselby</a></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-114c07c9-0 iNdsQY"><span>4,500<!-- --> words</span><span class="sc-114c07c9-2 hRWhru"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" width="17" height="17" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" data-cy="icon-aeon-save" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M17 3H7c-1.1 0-1.99.9-1.99 2L5 21l7-3 7 3V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 15l-5-2.18L7 18V5h10v13z"></path></svg><span>Save</span></span></div><br/><div class="sc-50e6fb3a-1 jUPTLs"><a class="sc-45649ee9-0 fOpabg sc-50e6fb3a-0 gZdfWA" href="/syndication?article_slug=the-first-world-orders-were-not-european-they-came-from-asia&amp;article_name=The%20Asian%20world%20order&amp;author=Ay%C5%9Fe%20Zarakol&amp;date=9%20January%202024"><span class="sc-45649ee9-1 cacrwE">Syndicate this <!-- -->essay</span></a></div><div class="sc-c3e98e6e-0 bSqqMf sc-3ddd79c0-13 kNGStK"><div class="sc-c3e98e6e-0 bSqqMf"><div><br/></div><div class="sc-531dc212-0 gowMUU"><div><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" width="20px" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" data-cy="icon-aeon-email" aria-hidden="true" class="sc-531dc212-1 dkebQC"><path d="M22 6c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2H4c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v12c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h16c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V6zm-2 0l-8 5-8-5h16zm0 12H4V8l8 5 8-5v10z"></path></svg><span class="sc-531dc212-2 gjonPf">Email</span></div><div><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" width="20px" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" data-cy="icon-aeon-save" aria-hidden="true" class="sc-531dc212-1 dkebQC"><path d="M17 3H7c-1.1 0-1.99.9-1.