a-cy="icon-aeon-comment-bubble" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21.303,16.553l1.107,3.783l-3.48-2.322c-0.689,0.234-1.422,0.371-2.193,0.371c-1.041,0-2.024-0.234-2.907-0.642 c2.034-1.697,3.333-4.275,3.333-7.166c0-1.994-0.625-3.836-1.677-5.347c0.406-0.073,0.823-0.117,1.251-0.117 c3.762,0,6.814,2.971,6.814,6.634c0,1.594-0.578,3.057-1.539,4.2L21.303,16.553z M15.255,10.684c0,3.861-3.213,6.99-7.176,6.99 c-0.812,0-1.583-0.144-2.31-0.391l-3.667,2.446l1.166-3.985l-0.744-0.638c-1.013-1.203-1.621-2.743-1.621-4.423 c0-3.858,3.215-6.987,7.176-6.987C12.042,3.696,15.255,6.825,15.255,10.684z"></path></svg></span></div></div></a><a href="/essays/the-earthquakes-that-shook-mexico-citys-sense-of-time"><div class="sc-d56bc236-9 gdveBl"><div type="essay" class="sc-82db9615-2 kVCsWP"><img alt="" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 960px) 45vw, (max-width: 1440px) 30vw, 430px" srcSet="https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/52e7af71-f072-4617-a4b4-ad4489c87fef/essay-gettyimages-852639904.jpg?width=256&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 256w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/52e7af71-f072-4617-a4b4-ad4489c87fef/essay-gettyimages-852639904.jpg?width=384&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 384w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/52e7af71-f072-4617-a4b4-ad4489c87fef/essay-gettyimages-852639904.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 640w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/52e7af71-f072-4617-a4b4-ad4489c87fef/essay-gettyimages-852639904.jpg?width=750&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 750w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/52e7af71-f072-4617-a4b4-ad4489c87fef/essay-gettyimages-852639904.jpg?width=828&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 828w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/52e7af71-f072-4617-a4b4-ad4489c87fef/essay-gettyimages-852639904.jpg?width=1080&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 1080w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/52e7af71-f072-4617-a4b4-ad4489c87fef/essay-gettyimages-852639904.jpg?width=1200&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 1200w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/52e7af71-f072-4617-a4b4-ad4489c87fef/essay-gettyimages-852639904.jpg?width=1920&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 1920w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/52e7af71-f072-4617-a4b4-ad4489c87fef/essay-gettyimages-852639904.jpg?width=2048&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 2048w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/52e7af71-f072-4617-a4b4-ad4489c87fef/essay-gettyimages-852639904.jpg?width=3840&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 3840w" src="https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/52e7af71-f072-4617-a4b4-ad4489c87fef/essay-gettyimages-852639904.jpg?width=3840&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto"/></div><div class="sc-d56bc236-1 bLA-dMf"><div class="sc-d56bc236-8 gArifC"><div class="sc-d56bc236-5 BJZni"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" width="20px" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" data-cy="icon-aeon-save" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M17 3H7c-1.1 0-1.99.9-1.99 2L5 21l7-3 7 3V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 15l-5-2.18L7 18V5h10v13z"></path></svg><span class="sc-d56bc236-4 gKlMxC">Save</span></div><p class="sc-d56bc236-0 sc-d56bc236-3 eNVkkS XNdEw">essay</p><p class="sc-d56bc236-0 sc-d56bc236-2 eNVkkS eSkyVL">Earth science and climate</p></div><p class="sc-d56bc236-10 tdBWn">When does after begin?</p><p class="sc-d56bc236-11 hYbLtW">Three earthquakes hit Mexico City on the same date in 1985, 2017 and 2022. The coincidence left the city stranded in time</p><p class="sc-d56bc236-0 sc-d56bc236-12 eNVkkS dFhhBp">Lachlan Summers</p></div><div class="sc-d56bc236-6 jrySry"></div></div></a></div></div></div></div><footer class="sc-9fa52143-0 ehWxvC footer" data-test="footer"><div class="sc-ae266dcd-0 sc-9fa52143-1 gNLkNi jiMqSk"><div class="sc-3a83d547-0 fiZvIr"><div class="sc-47bc2fa8-0 sc-bab0e3bb-0 fOjrTm dmJOTI"><nav class="sc-bab0e3bb-1 emlfmU"><a href="/essays" class="sc-3f04373c-0 cKjeGj">Essays</a><a href="/ideas" clas